  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Professor w. II. Burr OF New\nYork has for two days been en-.\ngagged in inspecting the plans and\nsite of the new Monroe street con-\ncrete bridge, in connection with\nCity Engineer Ralston.\n\n\nHe has not given out any of his\nconclusions, but will probably have\nhis report ready for submission to\nthe city council in day or two.\n\n\nCity Engineer Ralston, who drew\nthe plans. says he invites full\nand free criticism. and trusts the\nBurr report. viii go Into the matter\nON ITS merits."
    }
